  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a pan over medium-high heat.",
    "Add minced garlic and onions, sauté until softened.",
    "Toss in sliced fresh chili peppers if using.",
    "Stir in the tomato chunks and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Mix in doubanjiang, reduce to taste for desired tartness. Allow mixture to simmer gently for another 3-4 minutes.",
    "Adjust seasoning as needed with salt or soy sauce.",
    "Serve immediately while still hot."
